#NYPCluster UPDATES | WE ARE RE-OPENING THE CALL FOR APPLICATIONS FOR THE #13thNYP CLUSTER ASSEMBLY FOR NATIONAL CAPITAL REGION! 

Apply now to the 13th National Youth Parliament- Cluster 4 Assembly!

The National Youth Commission will be conducting the 13th National Youth Parliament- Cluster Assembly for NCR on February 21-23, 2025, in NCR.

The activity aims to:
* Gather active Filipino Youth to participate and engage in the 13th NATIONAL YOUTH PARLIAMENT â€“ CLUSTER ASSEMBLY;
* Discuss relevant issues concerning the Youth in the cluster; and to
* Formulate policy recommendations.

QUALIFICATIONS FOR THE 13th NATIONAL YOUTH PARLIAMENT â€“ CLUSTER ASSEMBLY (National Capital Region):
* Must be 15 â€“ 30 years old as of February 10, 2025; 
* Must not be a previous NYP Delegate;
* Preferably a member of a YORP registered organization/National Youth Volunteer Program;
* Must be actively involved in NYC activities, programs, and projects; &
* Must be a Filipino Citizen.

REQUIREMENTS FOR THE 13th NATIONAL YOUTH PARLIAMENT â€“ CLUSTER ASSEMBLY:
* Duly accomplished Application Form;
* Duly filled out committee preference questionnaire;
* Proof of Residency and Birth (any government-issued ID/student/company ID);
* Photocopy of any certificate received from any NYC Activities/Projects/Programs (if available);
* Photocopy of YORP/NYVP passports (if available).

DEADLINE FOR APPLICATION (13th NYP Assembly for Cluster 4) IS UNTIL February 10, 2025, 5:00 PM.

Apply now by scanning the QR Code below or you may access this link:
https://bit.ly/13THNYPCluster-4 

REMINDER: Only those who will participate in the NYP Cluster/Regional Assemblies will be able to apply and participate in the NYP National Assembly.

